title: Rumors circle about Ivanka and Jared's influence on Trump
text: Relaxed... for now! Ivanka and Jared enjoy a dressed down family day amid criticism over their failure to stop Trump's controversial reversal of the transgender bathroom bill Ivanka Trump stepped out with her family on Saturday in Washington, DC She and Jared may have influenced climate change and LGBT rights legislation The power couple are believed to have fought in favor of LGBT measures A report said Ivanka and Jared led the charge to keep the existing rules They were set up by Barack Obama in 2014 and protect LGBT federal workers
